000Z","msg":"呢個學者真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前已經整埋template聯絡自己州份既參議員同眾議員要求佢地支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果眾籌夠錢等喺WSJ同WaPo一定好有威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca4b2e7f318f5027fe4569c6b3013c234c388fa","tid":1379012,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"重要"},{"pid":"a310c65f6393116ccb76a5532fd4c2286e9fc8af","tid":1379012,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d34afecc6f5e4a8ef7a4f330f50113294e38ebf8","tid":1379012,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"民間外交最緊要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e65e3a1b5ed4afe2acd912632b28dfedfa2d3d","tid":1379012,"uid":78241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"both la <br />\n香港人課金世界第一"},{"pid":"f62b37d01b4758d0881eb0ce821fa37599a7d759","tid":1379012,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b875b23c77de3a4b9b8863fbddc2e9d73035e7d","tid":1379012,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:30.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad296c4ef47da93b729be70cdad112228d853aa","tid":1379012,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d1d5932552ad8f93a0466e99e89ac6a38abaee","tid":1379012,"uid":272371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ec9a9eb48439c816f0adec7d02fac9eb62ba0a","tid":1379012,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bd6d5c39d9019f839121a85f09fea6b2438e70","tid":1379012,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43c07dcd3d29f135e5608d7dacb445695ce96e7","tid":1379012,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50abc5041fa5aaeeb33cc46c0efd67912f29bca1","tid":1379012,"uid":248225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"如果聽日佢哋開會話出咩解放軍，停水停電，停工，大家唔洗理，當佢鳩UP。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最怕聽日係政府放軟小小態度，例如話林鄭辭職，又撤回法例甚至話畀普選等等。 <br />\n<br />\n我預計會有以下情況出現：<br />\n1. 有一班打手上水話要接受政府退步，運動要停止啦。 <br />\n<br />\n2.或者飯民又接受政府開出既條件。<br />\n<br />\n3.又或者社會媒體又吹和談風。<br />\n<br />\n由此至終，五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係第五點，我地唔要中共開出既普選，要有美國監督下既普選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚同聽日下午三點，文宣宣傳重申五大訴求，缺一不可。同時煲大今晚黑警罪行。<br />\n<br />\n咁辛苦走到呢步，唔可以因為政府小小甜頭而散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特此預告！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378852/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"27f831f4575f215dc197f6b32caa62f9130a0c58","tid":1379012,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:59.000Z","msg":"sir this way"},{"pid":"058e4c37db71b2beef03b16086e88e204fec810a","tid":1379012,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70722e6abaf31a46b8c706ad5fda078251bc05ee","tid":1379012,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"冷靜<br />\n唔好一瞳登報就俾正皮住<br />\n睇清楚寫乜<br />\n起一起嗰fb page底先"},{"pid":"b3bd1d2652fe4fe0974b2ce1ad33d6f1859ea9a6","tid":1379012,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌<br />\n唔好屌侵侵或任何美國政治人物<br />\n唔撚好干涉美國政治或結怨</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nUnfortunately, President Donald Trump has been reluctant to openly criticize such assaults on democratic values. Puzzlingly, he has instead suggested that President Xi Jinping of China had &quot;acted responsibly&quot;, calling for Hong Kong and China to &quot;resolve&quot; the matter themselves, thereby shrugging off any recommendation to intervene."},{"pid":"169706f76eca22dd31ae7be491d6f98941b82063","tid":1379012,"uid":125911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e70a86f0da1f5c7ec75581b6462777fcd7a36b1","tid":1379012,"uid":242386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n嚟多次半日幾球壯舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d5ec7d4e44e66c0506f014fd5b863428f6916b","tid":1379012,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"內容方向，除咗唔好屌侵侵，大致冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字眼或者可以再得體啲"},{"pid":"613665e050a6a141a6180b8af403e74c498b8056","tid":1379012,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12d5ec7d4e44e66c0506f014fd5b863428f6916b","tid":1379012,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"內容方向，除咗唔好屌侵侵，大致冇乜問題<img src=\